*''[[真穗猪笼草|N. eustachya]]'' × ''N. sumatrana''<ref name=Clarke />
*''[[小猪笼草|N. gracilis]]'' × ''N. sumatrana''<ref name=McPherson>McPherson, S.R. 2009. ''[[旧大陆的猪笼草|Pitcher Plants of the Old World]]''. 2 volumes. Redfern Natural History Productions, Poole.</ref>
